---
  layout: layouts/_base.njk
---

{% from 'minipost.njk' import miniPost %}

<article class="w-index mx-auto mt-4 sm:mt-6 px-6 sm:px-0">
  <h2 class="mb-4 mt-0 text-4xl">Hello! 💐</h2>

  <p>My real name is <span class="font-bold text-beach-watermelon">Erika</span> but maybe you know me under the nickname <span class="font-semibold text-pinky-unicorny">Princesseuh</span> 👸, that's okay!</p>

  <p>I'm a web/game developer from Canada 🇨🇦, pleased to meet you! Truth be told, I'm not as interested in programming as I once used to be, however, I'm definitely still a nerd at heart and having your own website is still a really cool thing, so hey, welcome to my website! Feel free to browse around!</p>

  Interested in seeing stuff I worked on? Click <a href="/projects/">here for my projects</a>! Wanna read stuff I wrote? Well, lucky you, <a href="/articles/">here's my blog</a>! You want to read random stuff I wrote mostly for myself? Well, <a href="/wiki/">my wiki is right here</a>!&nbsp;🎉

  <h3 class="text-2xl mb-5">Featured works</h3>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap mx-10 mt-2 mb-6 gap-5 sm:gap-4 justify-center items-center">
    {%- for project in collections.project | featured -%}
    <div class="h-[180px] relative">
      <a href="{{ project.url }}">
        {% set cover = "projects/"+ project.data.type + "s/" + project.fileSlug + "/cover.png" %}
        {% cover cover, "Eleventy's logo. 11 ty", undefined %}
        <h4 class="cover-title">
          {{ project.data.title }}
        </h4>
      </a>
    </div>
    {%- endfor -%}
  </div>

  <div class="flex justify-around gap-4 flex-col sm:flex-row">
    <div class="sm:w-[63%]">
      <h3 class="text-2xl mb-4 mt-2 sm:mt-4">Latest blog posts</h3>
      {%- for post in collections.post | reverse -%}
      {% if (loop.index <= 3) %}
      {{ miniPost(post) }}
      {% endif %}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>

    <div class="sm:w-[37%]">
      <h3 class="text-2xl mb-4 mt-2 sm:mt-4">Latest wiki modifications</h3>
      {%- for page in collections.latestWiki -%}
      {% if (loop.index <= 5) %}
      <section class="mb-3">
        <a class="block font-bold leading-tight" href="{{ page.url }}">
          {{ page.data.title }}
        </a>
        <span class="text-sm" data-date="{{ page.data.lastModified }}">
          {{ (page.data.lastModified | readableDatetime).slice(0, -3) }}
        </span>
      </section>
      {% endif %}
      {%- endfor -%}
    </div>
  </div>
</article>
